{"tid":1691362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請所有仲有良心既cctvb員工立即辭職","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T03:18:39.000Z","uid":90601,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5c00d594ee48c87d46c82ab63c89a84ac47599","tid":1691362,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1678608719047846/photos/a.1764177917157592/2442621495979894/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1678608719047846%2Fphotos%2Fa.1764177917157592%2F2442621495979894%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=d2a0bfcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1678608719047846/photos/a.1764177917157592/2442621495979894/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n平時點洗白黑警已經夠過份<br />\n今晚太古血案 cctvb直頭係幫凶手既行凶意圖同手法消曬毒<br />\ntouch wood講句 如果有手足真係出事<br />\n你地就係幫凶 係同凶手同一陣線 成世人良心都唔會過意去<br />\n<br />\n做傳媒唔同做黑警/消防 唔洗驚無左份工之後搵唔返<br />\n而且香港做傳媒本來就係血汗工場 等上位十世都唔會有你份 上面班老屎忽食古不化 <br />\n你地甘願為左少少人工 埋沒良心咩?<br />\n今日之後你地敢唔敢同人講你做cctvb?<br />\n抬得起頭做人咩?<br />\n<br />\n你甘願做狗 我無話可說 如果你地仲有人性 唔該打定辭職信即刻辭職"},{"pid":"9c07735d116365a85eb18c24526a757be4560978","tid":1691362,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8df64157e354f1e59efd1c1afb205c0594cd3c2","tid":1691362,"uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"點解TVB仲咁撚串？因為狙擊Group 得個6千人follow，我今晚要見到過萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9cae54750a91c57eb1d60f3d050e59024f5470d6","tid":1691362,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:36:04.000Z","msg"